s of the child to visit the station or call the number provided. Vanguard News Nigeria    By Ikechukwu Odu Unknown gunmen, Friday morning allegedly killed yet-to-be-identified police personnel attached to Nsukka Police Division at a checkpoint located at Umeano Junction, Nsukka Local Government Area of Enugu State. The unknown gunmen equally proceeded to another police checkpoint at Ibagwa-Ani, also in Nsukka Local Government Area where they… In "Metro" No casualty on shooting at checkpoint in Enugu- Police In "News" The Police Command in Enugu State said it has found the car of missing Nollywood actress, Cynthia Okereke In "News"